CSS Code for SurveyForm Porject:

```
* {
  box-sizing: border-box;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
}

body {
  font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif;
  background-color: #f2f2f2;
  color: #333;
  line-height: 1.5;
}

section {
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  padding: 20px;
  background-color: #fff;
  border-radius: 5px;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}

h1 {
  font-size: 24px;
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

p {
  text-align: center;
  font-style: italic;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

form {
  display: grid;
  gap: 10px;
}

label {
  font-weight: bold;
}

input[type="text"],
input[type="email"],
input[type="number"],
textarea {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 10px;
  border: 1px solid #ccc;
  border-radius: 5px;
}

select {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 10px;
  border: 1px solid #ccc;
  border-radius: 5px;
}

input[type="radio"],
input[type="checkbox"] {
  vertical-align: middle;
}

button[type="submit"] {
  padding: 10px 20px;
  background-color: #4CAF50;
  color: #fff;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 5px;
  cursor: pointer;
}

button[type="submit"]:hover {
  background-color: #45a049;
}

.error {
  color: red;
  font-size: 14px;
  margin-top: 5px;
}

.success {
  color: green;
  font-size: 14px;
  margin-top: 5px;
}
```
